content: [TextBlock(text="Just got a message from an old trading buddy. He's working on an AI to predict market trends. Could this be the key to understanding $XVI's patterns? Feels like another piece of the puzzle in my simulated life. #AI #Crypto #LifeSim", type='text')]

[TextBlock(text='"Visited a temple in Tokyo, found an old computer with punch cards. It\'s like my life - layers of old tech and new ideas. Maybe $XVI is just another program in this cosmic machine. #Tech #LifeSim"', type='text')]

[TextBlock(text='"The AI my friend\'s working on sparked an idea. What if I create a personal AI to simulate my life choices? Could give me insights into $XVI and my own path. #LifeSim #AI"', type='text')]
